  "description": "<p>A high-end, comfortable climbing harness for technical routes and alpine climbing. Tricked out with a host of thoughtful features, it uses Fuseframe construction to produce a very slim, clean, lightweight harness.</p><ul><li>Fuseframe construction distributes weight over the structure and minimizes pressure points</li><li>Fused fabric and foam layers have no crossing seams to help prevent friction zones</li><li>TPU reinforcements on lower leg loops add durability</li><li>DoubleBack aluminum HD buckles have a slim, rounded design that offers good grip and fluid glide on the waist and leg loop webbing</li><li>Adjustable leg loops have elastic at the front for mobility and flexibility</li><li>5 equipment loops: rigid in front for quick and easy access to equipment and flexible in the rear to avoid creating pressure points with a backpack</li><li>Compatible with Caritool Evo</li><li>Reinforced tie-in points</li></ul>",
